 {"id":"bd-321","title":"Convert decode API functions to return Result instead of panicking","description":"The decode module has 4+ intentional panics that should be converted to Result returns: decode_from_lines(), decode_stream_sync(), decode_stream() in src/decode/mod.rs. These are public API functions that currently panic on errors rather than returning Result<T>.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-21T10:23:22.238952088Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-21T10:40:02.931750466Z","closed_at":"2026-01-21T10:40:02.931706383Z","close_reason":"Added try_decode, try_decode_from_lines, try_decode_stream_sync, try_decode_stream functions that return Result<T>. The original functions now delegate to the try_ versions and panic on error. All 24 tests pass, clippy clean.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
